From 71350145472493c2d7f5ea8ce3eb64e66bdd4601 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Barra <dev@procexai.tech>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 02:44:02 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] feat(send/media): support viewOnce for image, video and audio

Adds an optional `viewOnce` flag to POST /send/media (JSON and multipart).
When set, the media message is marked with the inner `viewOnce` field and
wrapped in `ViewOnceMessageV2`, which is what current WhatsApp clients render
as the one-time-view badge.

The wrap happens after ContextInfo (quote, mentions, forwarding) is applied,
so replies keep working. Non-media types and newsletters ignore the flag.
---
 pkg/sendMessage/handler/send_handler.go   |  6 ++-
 pkg/sendMessage/service/send_service.go   | 43 ++++++++++++++++++
 pkg/sendMessage/service/view_once_test.go | 53 +++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 101 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
 create mode 100644 pkg/sendMessage/service/view_once_test.go

